creator: zboot
descriptionHtml:
Tired of all those inaccessible website that are blocked in your region?
Really need to browse the Internet without worrying too much?
You want speed, security and reliability?

z vpn is the solution for you.

Light weight, fast and simple design. You can connect to different locations. Other locations will also be added in the future.

How to use it?

◾ Launch the app
◾ Select the location you want to use (or select Auto mode)
◾ And click on the shield on the screen
◾ Accept the app to use system's VPN
◾ Wait for the app to connect to server

That's it!

This apps features also:

◾ Multiple servers to choose from
◾ Individually select which apps are allowed to use the VPN server
◾ Light and Dark mode
◾ Other features will be added soon
descriptionShort: Browse the Internet Freely and Securely

title: z vpn: unlimited web access

creator: zboot
descriptionHtml:
Tired of all those inaccessible website that are blocked in your region?
Really need to browse the Internet without worrying too much?
You want to play your favorite games without any issues?
You want speed, security and reliability?

z vpn is the solution for you.

Light weight, fast and simple design. You can connect to different locations. Other locations will also be added in the future.

How to use it?

◾ Launch the app
◾ Select the location you want to use (or select Auto mode)
◾ And click on the shield on the screen
◾ Accept the app to use system's VPN
◾ Wait for the app to connect to server

That's it!

This apps features also:

◾ Multiple servers to choose from
◾ Individually select which apps are allowed to use the VPN server
◾ Light and Dark mode
◾ Other features will be added soon

On our app we focus on Security and connection Speeds. We always work hard with our partners to provide best VPN servers around the world. Our VPN servers are always maintained to keep them running smoothly and without any problems.
We also focus on Security and Privacy. Your data is transmitted safely throughout our VPN networks. We use latest encryption technologies to ensure the safety of your data and transaction history.

We keep almost zero log of connection and visited websites. Some data is stored briefly on our servers to ensure service quality. But this data will never leave our servers and will never be retained more than one week.

Our VPN networks are also optimized for Gaming. We offer very low latency for First-Person Shooter (FPS) games so you can play games seamlessly and smoothly. You can also use z vpn to play your favorite censored games all around the world.

We offer many locations to connect to: United States of America, France, Italy, Germany, Singapore, Australia and many more to come in the future.

You can also subscribe to our services for a very cheap price, and you get free access to all servers without any ads and limitations.

z vpn is also supported on Android TV devices so you can watch your favorite shows or play your games without censorship and on all types of Android TVs.
descriptionShort: Unlimited VPN Proxy : Play Games & Browse the Internet Freely and Securely
